  "keyFeatures": [
    "55+ accessible React components built on Radix UI primitives",
    "Vanilla CSS styling with HTML data-attributes for flexible theming",
    "Enterprise-ready data tables with sorting, filtering, and virtualization",
    "Full TypeScript support with comprehensive type definitions",
    "Dark mode support with theme provider and switcher components",
    "Comprehensive icon set and reusable hooks library"
